{"tid":475433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅磡海面女浮屍　警證為17歲失蹤少女","createTime":"2017-11-21T06:13:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-22T06:35:55.000Z","uid":20933,"like":25,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"6e023a0c5a9f5d0117dfabd07a1f3b978d01ddda","tid":475433,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T06:13:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171121/large/1511241958_ad55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171121%2Flarge%2F1511241958_ad55.jpg&h=4b02f974&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方調查後證實，昨日在紅磡環海街發現的女性浮屍，為報失的17歲少女錢宇凝。<br />\n<br />\n昨午1時20分，負責海上清潔的船隻工人，在紅磡環海街7號對開海面，發現一名女子在水中載浮載沉，於是報警。消防蛙人到場將女子救起，證實已告不治。死者身穿灰色及黑色間條上衣，藍色牛仔褲及黑色運動鞋( <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2zUE0jN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2zUE0jN&d=zW8s0yBelm5wq9enpmvRSAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=fa37e7a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2zUE0jN</a> )。<br />\n<br />\n昨晚警方亦發圖呼籲，指17歲少女錢宇凝前日離開其港島西半山巴丙頓道的住所後失蹤，家人昨日報案( <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2zjYDXu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2zjYDXu&d=zW8s0yBelm5wq9enpmvRSAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=230bc61c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2zjYDXu</a> )。警方經調查，證實為同一人。"},{"pid":"6faeb4e069b05e810d6502402c1e2d9484993c8c","tid":475433,"uid":13802,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T06:14:23.000Z","msg":"樣都出埋"},{"pid":"64f6df0ffc194b75f2b1fc4f011c35ac3e43cdf1","tid":475433,"uid":146604,"like":9,"dislike":9,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T06:15:20.000Z","msg":"有錢女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6443c25c708d8a40cdc98f9f5ac57dd46807031","tid":475433,"uid":116530,"like":2,"dislike":31,"score":-29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T06:16:31.000Z","msg":"索野索到死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6674d0d98063