回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"877125ea83cadce439727102af0c37e061ab43d9","tid":475433,"uid":34394,"like":110,"dislike":3,"score":107,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T00:58:51.000Z","msg":"佢係我同學嚟，平時份人比較內向，冇乜朋友，可能有啲壓力冇人同佢分擔，所以諗埋咗一邊 有咩事真係要同人講，唔好收收埋埋<br />\n<br />\n 願錢同學安息，她的家人與身邊的同學都可以共同渡過這難關<br />\n<br />\n有錢唔代表冇壓力 唔係咩都係錢咁簡單的"},{"pid":"e8129ce59c676abd0643b1f6b49d328cf7714ff2","tid":475433,"uid":23902,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T01:02:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真心問其實住半山都到左終點   平時生活有咩做？</blockquote><br />\n知你波台假膠 但係自己用腦諗下ok?"},{"pid":"30375586b0c576ea2c7cb5bf6724cfdfe50cb812","tid":475433,"uid":39151,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T01:03:46.000Z","msg":"有時唔係錢咁簡單架 壓力個個都有 個個都有唔同程度<br />\n樓上個啲 就算佢住半山又點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"555592ae6345486dc611d92a80b01dfd0b1df10f","tid":475433,"uid":140879,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T01:40:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抵啦</blockquote><br />\n你有冇人性架屌你老母"},{"pid":"663b4a24026917558450322bb406bdfd4d194180","tid":475433,"uid":34103,"like":2,"dislike":35,"score":-33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T01:43:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"37ee4b3bdc7de86e7e5f756c010cac9d779312b9","tid":475433,"uid":27568,"like":34,"dislike":2,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T01:49:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢係我同學嚟，平時份人比較內向，冇乜朋友，可能有啲壓力冇人同佢分擔，所以諗埋咗一邊 有咩事真係要同人講，唔好收收埋埋<br />\n<br />\n 願錢同學安息，她的家人與身邊的同學都可以共同渡過這難關<br />\n<br />\n有錢唔代表冇壓力 唔係咩都係錢咁簡單的</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錢唔代表無壓力<br />\n但無錢肯定更大壓力"},{"pid":"37fd52a2e56096003be2fc0b7a2f5c43c045fd31","tid":475433,"uid":22231,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T01:57:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁柒，是但啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fbddb4c0ebcf38cfb8b442f27c49617e91693c1","tid":475433,"uid":47647,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T02:00:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁柒，是但啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好撚賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab6a45ff8a81aefb035a3c755c78f5ab2bb53653","tid":475433,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T02:01:13.000Z","msg":"其實點樣咁多拖條屍掉落去<br />\n放上車 去到 倒垃圾咁 ?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲監控真係  幾百單同樣棄屍都黎緊<br />\n香港咁撚細  都咁樣玩到 真係on9<br />\n然後發現就 查唔撚到  垃撚圾 掉左落海先查 <br />\n海邊set多啲cam都得啦"},{"pid":"6dd5acf408b37f2410e0eac5246329e47c1c3a5f","tid":475433,"uid":1082,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T02:01:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真心問其實住半山都到左終點   平時生活有咩做？</blockquote><br />\n山頂係目的短淺既窮人黎講係終點，但係目光遠大既窮人同有錢佬心目中根本不值一提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f7fe76b259a2e01c8f428f5948b1e4a014c5e82","tid":475433,"uid":21260,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T02:02:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時唔係錢咁簡單架 壓力個個都有 個個都有唔同程度<br />\n樓上個啲 就算佢住半山又點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁係因為佢唔知唔係住半山個啲係慘過死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申窮L"},{"pid":"008b16f60acb25393ef725ebfe81be78202504df","tid":475433,"uid":25214,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T02:14:58.000Z","msg":"咁有錢都自殺 哂撚哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"570f8e49a41f45af9da0